		</section>
        <section>
            <div class="container mt-5 mb-5" id="about-proper">
                <div class="row " id="mission">
                    <div class="col-md d-flex justify-content-center mt-3 mb-3">
                        <img src="logo2.png" alt="Logo">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md mt-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="mission-title">Our Mission</div>

                        <div class="mission-text">
                            <br>
                            The mission of Terra is to be one of the world's leading producers of eco-fashion bag.  The brand promotes an environment-friendly, high-quality multipurpose bag which creates a unique fashion that is perfect for on-the-go modern Filipinas. </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row mt-3 mb-3" id="advocacy">
                    <div class="advocacy-title">Advocacy and Collaborations</div>
                    <div class="mission-text"> 
                    <br>
                    Terra Philippines is start-up eco-fashion business that recently won 2 major awards at the JA Asia-Pacific business competition: <b>Company of the Year </b> and <b>FedEx Access Award </b>. <br>
                    <br>
                    The Isla Bag, an environment-friendly, high-quality multipurpose bag was featured in different newspapers, radios and television including:
                    <br>
                    <b>PhilStar, Philippine Daily Inquirer, Manila Bulletin, DZRH, Radyo Negosyo, GMA</b> and many more.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="row mt-3 mb-3" id="ambassadors">
                    <div class="ambassadors-title">Ambassadors</div>
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    <div class="amb-text">
                        <br>
                    <br> <h3 id="amb-name">Alaina Carlize Tria</h3>   
                    <br> <h4 id="amb-pos"><i>Chief Executive Officer</i></h4>
                    <br><br>

                    <br> <h3 id="amb-name">Gwen Villaver</h3>  <br> 
                    <h4 id="amb-pos"><i>Marketing Executive Vice President </i></h4>
                    <br><br>

                    <br> <h3 id="amb-name">Raphaella Mae Sanchez</h3> <br> 
                    <h4 id="amb-pos"><i>Executive Vice President for Human Resources</i></h4>
                    <br><br>
                    
                    <br> <h3 id="amb-name">Porsha Mangilit</h3> <br> 
                    <h4 id="amb-pos"><i>Corporate Secretary</i></h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row" id="contact">
                    <div class="col-md d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                        <div class="contact-title">Contact Us</div>
                        <div class="contact-email">Email: terrarelations@gmail.com</div>
                        <div class="contact-number">Contact number: 0908 895 2932</div>
                        <div class="contact-icons d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/terraphils"><img src="fb-icon.png" alt="Facebook Icon" class="sm-icon"></a>
                            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/terra_phils/"><img src="insta-icon.png" alt="Instagram Icon" class="sm-icon"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md">
                        <form class="modal-content"  method="post">
                            <div class="container-form"> 
                                <label id="form-text"for="email"><b>Email</b></label>
                                <input type="email" placeholder="Enter Email" id="email" name="email" value={{email}} required>

                                <label id="form-text"for="mobile_no"><b>Mobile Number</b></label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Mobile Number" id="mobile_no" name="mobile_no" required>

                                <label id="form-text"for="name"><b>Name</b></label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Enter Name" name="name" id="name" required>

                                <label id="form-text"for="message"><b>Message</b></label>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="Your Message" id="message" name="message" required>
                                
                                <button type="submit" class="submit">Submit</button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <button onclick="topFunction()" id="top-button" title="Go to top">Top</button>
        </section>
        <script type="text/javascript">
            mybutton = document.getElementById("top-button");

            // When the user scrolls down 20px from the top of the document, show the button
            window.onscroll = function() {scrollFunction()};

            function scrollFunction() {
              if (document.body.scrollTop > 20 || document.documentElement.scrollTop > 20) {
                mybutton.style.display = "block";
              } else {
                mybutton.style.display = "none";
              }
            }

            // When the user clicks on the button, scroll to the top of the document
            function topFunction() {
              document.body.scrollTop = 0; // For Safari
              document.documentElement.scrollTop = 0; // For Chrome, Firefox, IE and Opera
            }
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
